snippet.title: Stellar Poetry (Full Demo) | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Stellar Poetry is a 2D action adventure game similar to the galaxy Castlevania. The sorceress, who awakens after sensing the call of a mysterious voice, goes on a series of adventures in order to find memories lost due to the curse.

Game by MXL-Studio
Game Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2993550/Stellar_Poetry/

#StellarPoetry #MXLStudio #IndieGame
